interest waiver on education loan and 2% interest waiver on Shishu Mudra Loans will help poor people to a great extent.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/covid-19-haryana-announces-to-waive-three-months-interest-on-education-loan/articleshow/75854419.cms  at  "}